OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a dry start rain will
OL,6,Fspread southeastwards across all parts
OL,7,Ffor a time. Drier weather with a few
OL,8,Fshowers following on behind for the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Mild this morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA few showers this evening.
OL,12,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,13,Fwith clear periods and just the odd
OL,14,Fshower. Cold with patchy frost.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FThe morning will be dry.
OL,17,FRain will spread east across all parts
OL,18,Fduring the afternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
